properties.Name: LienAttachedAsset
properties.Description: The asset(s) attached in conjunction with the associated Lien.

Columns.Name: LienId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Lien.

Columns.Name: AssetId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Asset.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date that the asset is attached to the lien.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date that the asset is attached to the lien.

Columns.Name: AttachedAppraisedAssetValueAmount
Columns.Description: The appraised value of the Lien attached collateral assets.

Columns.Name: AttachedAssetOrderedSoldDate
Columns.Description: The date that the attached asset was ordered sold.

Columns.Name: AttachedAssetSoldDate
Columns.Description: The date that the attached asset was sold.

Columns.Name: AttachedAssetSoldAmount
Columns.Description: The amount for which the attached asset was sold.

Columns.Name: LienAttachedAssetNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information related to a attached lien asset.

Columns.Name: AttachedAssetStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Attached Asset Status.
